    <section id="id7574542">
      <title>POEMS AND POETRY</title>
      <para id="id7574549">1. Poems for inspiration</para>
      <para id="id7574560">Your teacher is going to read some poems to you, which you will discuss in the class.</para>
      <para id="id7574564">What to do</para>
      <list id="id7574568" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Use all the inspiration from poems, as well as group and class discussions, to prepare a SPEECH entitled ‘It boggles my mind!’</item>
        <item>Obviously you need to choose something you truly find amazing and WOW your audience into being boggled by your information and deliverance too.</item>
        <item>Plan your speech (2 to 3 minutes) below. </item>
      </list>
