      <para id="id7718529"> 4. WORDPOWER</para>
      <para id="id7718535">Now it is time to create something amazing</para>
      <para id="id7718539">Time to change</para>
      <para id="id7718544"> Change one letter in each word to make a new word. Use the clues.</para>
