    <section id="id7596355">
      <title>Memorandum</title>
      <para id="id7596362">1. Poems for inspiration</para>
      <para id="id7596368">For the educator:</para>
      <list id="id7596373" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Use poems of your choice, as inspiration for SPEAKING as well as WRITING activities. </item>
        <item>Allow for group discussion as well as open class discussion on ‘Amazing things I have seen / heard / read.’</item>
        <item>The poems and discussions serve as inspiration for individual speech on ‘It boggles my mind!’</item>
        <item>The poems and discussions serve as inspiration for personal writing entitled ‘What amazes me.’</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id7596412">Encourage learners to write and talk about the obvious (metamorphosis) as well as the deeper changes (transformations).</para>
